title: 86. Self-worth & Money Mindset
description:
Hey sis!

In this episode, we are talking all about money mindset. If you are feeling triggered by the name of this episode or even by the word money, you are going to find this episode to be transformational as I go DEEP into the concept of how money, trauma, and self-worth are ALL related. Prepare for a breakthrough this week.
